page.title: 12QUESTIONAIRE - Intro cont.
page.content:
We have also seen a change in the type of housing.In the area we have studied the housing consists of typical ribbon development, of stone terraced housing along the main roads. Since the late 1970's we have seen two large,private housing estates built which are continuing to expand.
{RESULTS ******* The results are presented as follows:-
The questions asked are shown first, followed by the results shown in blue. All the results are given as percentages in order to try to allow comparisons to made more easily.
